<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{sae}}</strong> is a particle meaning "even".

<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{kono@KJ{{question^topic}}ha@KJ{{before^life}}de<strong>sae</strong>@KJ{{solution}}erarenakatta.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Even the teacher couldn't answer that quaestion.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</p>

<p>
<a name="if-only"><strong>@HI{{sae}}</strong></a>, when coupled with @Vta{{}}@HI{{ra}} or @Vba{{}} or @HI{{nara}},
means "if only" something had been done a positive result would have followed.

<ol>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{mou5@KJ{{part}}<strong>sae</strong>attara,@KJ{{fly^going^mechanism}}ni@KJ{{interval}}ni@KJ{{fit}}ttanoni.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      If only we had had 5 minutes more, we would have been in time for the flight.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{kono@KJ{{attend^matter}}<strong>sae</strong>@KJ{{one-sided^adhere}}itara@KJ{{behind}}ha@KJ{{music}}nandesu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      If we can just finish this work, the rest will be easy.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</ol>
</p>

